sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client<br/>(UI / SDK / CLI)
    participant API as API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP<br/>8887/TCP gRPC
    participant MySQL as MySQL<br/>3306/TCP
    participant MinIO as MinIO / S3<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Tekton as Tekton Controller
    participant Runner as Pipeline Runner Pod<br/>SA: pipeline-runner
    participant Cache as Cache Server<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant PA as Persistence Agent<br/>gRPC client
    participant SWC as Scheduled Workflow<br/>Controller
    participant Viz as Visualization Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP

    Note over Client,Viz: Flow 1: Pipeline Execution

    Client->>API: POST /apis/v1beta1/runs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    API->>MySQL: Store run metadata<br/>3306/TCP Username/Password
    API->>MinIO: Fetch pipeline template<br/>Access Key/Secret
    API->>K8sAPI: Create PipelineRun<br/>TLS, ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI->>Tekton: Reconcile PipelineRun
    Tekton->>K8sAPI: Create TaskRun Pods

    Note over K8sAPI,Cache: Flow 2: Cache Hit Check

    K8sAPI->>Cache: MutatingWebhook /mutate<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS, Webhook cert
    Cache->>MySQL: Query execution_caches<br/>3306/TCP Username/Password
    alt Cache Hit
        Cache-->>K8sAPI: Mutated pod spec<br/>(minimal image, cached outputs)
    else Cache Miss
        Cache-->>K8sAPI: Unmodified pod spec
        K8sAPI->>Runner: Create TaskRun Pod<br/>ServiceAccount token
        Runner->>MinIO: Store artifacts<br/>Access Key/Secret
        Runner->>K8sAPI: Complete TaskRun
    end

    Note over PA,API: Flow 3: Status Sync

    PA->>K8sAPI: Watch PipelineRuns<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, ServiceAccount
    K8sAPI-->>PA: PipelineRun status event
    PA->>API: ReportWorkflow (gRPC)<br/>8887/TCP, internal
    PA->>API: ReportRunMetrics (HTTP)<br/>8888/TCP, internal

    Note over SWC,K8sAPI: Flow 4: Scheduled Workflow

    SWC->>K8sAPI: Watch ScheduledWorkflow CRs<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, ServiceAccount
    K8sAPI-->>SWC: ScheduledWorkflow event
    SWC->>K8sAPI: Create PipelineRun<br/>on cron/periodic schedule

    Note over Client,Viz: Flow 5: Visualization

    Client->>API: POST /apis/v1beta1/visualizations<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    API->>Viz: POST visualization request<br/>8888/TCP HTTP, no auth
    Viz->>MinIO: Fetch artifacts<br/>Access Key/Secret
    Viz-->>API: HTML visualization
    API-->>Client: Visualization response
